reference "fig: bnp och lycka-1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

 where we see data for happiness and income in 2017 in all the world's countries.
 Each dot represents a combined value of happiness and gross national product per inhabitant,
 GDP per capita,
 that is average amount of total income per inhabitant.
\end_layout

