\begin_layout Standard
For our calculations,
 we will here again use the same made up observations for the variables 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 as in the previous chapter,
 which are repeated in figure 
