This we also see in the sums of the squared residuals.
 The higher value for 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum\hat{e_{t}}^{2}$
\end_inset

 compared to 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum\hat{\epsilon}_{t}^{2}$
\end_inset

