\end_inset

.
 This also means that the difference between the two slope coefficients in the regression models for women and men respectively is 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{b}-\hat{d}=0.2391-0.3818=-0.1427$
\end_inset

,
 which is the same value that we found for 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{c}_{4}$
\end_inset

 in equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
