\begin_layout Standard
The two regression models are illustrated in figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig: RDD med Carpenter och Dobkin"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

 where both graphs use the same data,
 obtained from Carpenter and Dobkin 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citeyearpar
key "carpenterEffectAlcoholConsumption2009"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Foot
status open

