\series default
 Suppose we have two random variables X and Y.
 The outcome in the two variables is determined simultaneously,
 at the same time,
 and do not affect each other.
 Say for example that we roll two dice where the result of one die does not affect the other and we are interested in the dice's total point sum.
\end_layout

