\begin_layout Standard
The chart is created with one of the common presets available in Excel.
 It is possible to change the appearance and colors in many ways by,
 for example,
 selecting all or parts of the chart and clicking in the Chart Design or Format menus,
 and for example choosing among the options Quick Layout,
