\begin_layout Standard
Another function that can be used to describe the values in a quantitative column (variable) is 
\family typewriter
tabstat
\family default
.
 With the help of the option statistics() we can define what type of measures we want to display.
 Here is an example,
 whose result is illustrated in figure 
