 We can also add different options to influence how the results are presented.
 Here follows another example with several options.
 We start with the command 
\family typewriter
eststo clear
\family default
,
 which clears the memory from results saved with eststo.
 If we do not clear the memory,
 
\family typewriter
eststo
\family default
 continues to save new tables together with old results.
 
