\end_inset

 describes our data with GDP per capita for the years 2015–2019.
 To create a table with these observations and variables in R we can use the following command:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\family typewriter
bnp_data <- tibble(
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\family typewriter
\begin_inset Formula $\qquad$
\end_inset

 year = 2015:2019,
 
